\begin_layout Section*
Descriptive Analysis
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This sections describes the development of job postings with the option
 of working remotely in the period 2008-2020.
 To our best knowledge, there does not currently exist an analysis of the
 remote labour market in Denmark, and we will therefore describe this in
 details below.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Noget om k-means
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
Graphical Analysis
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We start by looking at the overall trend in job postings published to Jobindex
 in both actual and relative numbers.
 
\series bold
Figure 3
\series default
 shows the monthly trend in the number of remote job postings and the total
 number of job postings on Jobindex in the period 2010-2020.
\end_layout

